,"msg":"有,不過今日下晝12點截左"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T09:26:17.000Z","msg":"尋日搞掂抽20手<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ba80fddb298be0549c9ec6ec0b55fe3d6f96c65","tid":597844,"uid":64935,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T09:33:23.000Z","msg":"2018年3月20日  17:11    新股新聞<br />\n<br />\n&lt;匯港通訊&gt;   雜誌《100毛》及毛記電視的母公司毛記葵涌(01716)及香港數碼媒體公司源想集團(08401)今日孖展截止,其中毛記孖展認購進一步升溫,據8間券商,合共為其借出259.45億元孖展額,相當於公開發售集資810萬元計,超購認購逾3202倍,較本港史上超購王 Magnum(02080)(現改名為奧克斯國際)的3558.2倍,只欠約356倍,相信可於明日中午截止公開發售後,順利坐上王者寶座,惟能否垗戰超購4000倍的大關,亦有待觀察。<br />\n<br />\n不過,由於毛記超購倍數驚人,故今日有投資者已知難而退,抽飛離場。據國泰君安指,<span style=\"color: red;\"> 有投資者因知道難中,故今日抽飛</span>,令其孖展認購由3億元減至2.7億元。<br />\n<br />\n毛記共錄得1076張「頂頭槌」飛(每張約818萬元),其中486張來自耀才、430張來自輝立、160張來自時富。  (見下表) (BC)<br />\n<br />\n知難而退<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80946211876ac5d2c4f86601eb645cf309f09950","tid":597844,"uid":166462,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T10:21:15.000Z","msg":"抽10萬股<br />\n有機會1手都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39d16965e90299b8cec35360165da8982874b8b9","tid":597844,"uid":170255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e1210ebd6ec0e7272474feaff1565fe6f6fb39c4","tid":597844,"uid":19322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T09:17:38.000Z","msg":"渣打直頭冇做毛記ipo<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T10:21:23.000Z","msg":"打電話咪有囉..."},{"pid":"c90e5f5311bbd7927a63f6de5d91c4bffe83606a","tid":597844,"uid":170255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8c0c98004108fa583327cc417e198c72888e558b","tid":597844,"uid":44808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e1210ebd6ec0e7272474feaff1565fe6f6fb39c4","tid":597844,"uid":19322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T